data.description:
Modern Features and Solar Panels!
Welcome to your dream home! This charming and  spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath gem with stone veneer boasts over 2300 square feet of living space and is perfect for families seeking comfort, convenience, and energy efficiency. Located just 15 minutes from Fort Bliss and a mere 10 minutes from the new William Beaumont Hospital, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a beautifully designed interior featuring granite countertops throughout and double sinks, providing both style and functionality. The owner's suite on the main level is a retreat of its own, complete with a separate shower and bath for your relaxation. The heart of this home is the open-concept kitchen, featuring a spacious island that seamlessly flows into the dining and living areas. This layout is perfect for hosting gatherings and making cherished memories with loved ones. Closing cost assistance & home warranty offered!
